➜实操Amazon相同账号不同站点如何共享A+页面编辑权
http://www.sohu.com/a/423515274_115514	42696
<p><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201009/0f04bbbcb3144bfabdfc5cbe0afeda4c.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span>遇到的问题是中东站和美国站使用了相同邮箱注册的，一套资料，美国站品牌备案账户授权给中东站的时候，由于授权是要输入邮箱的，亚马逊是按照邮箱授权，相同邮箱意味着同一个br账号（品牌账户),导致一直授权不成功，中东站就没办法做A+和品牌旗舰店。</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201009/fe1d7167b0f948578264a1532e4d2dab.png" /></p>
<p><span>先把case内容贴在这里，这是一遍过的写法：</span><span>我是中东站，你们替换成自己的站点，</span></p>
<p>The U.S. has already brand, and now I hope that the newly registered Middle East site can also get the permission to edit the listing.</p>
<p>The Middle East and American stations have different MCID, but they are registered with the same mailbox. Now we need to authorize the MCID of the Middle East station</p>
<p>The Middle East site account needs to have the editing permission of A+ page,</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p><span>●</span>http://amazon.com ------ Brand registration account: 我的美国站账户</p>
<p><span>●</span>American Station Merchant Token ：美国站 授权的品牌备案账户的商家令牌</p>
<p>amazon.ae ------ Authorized account:中东站账户</p>
<p>●Middle East Station Merchant Token：我的中东站账户商家令牌</p>
<p><span>●</span>Enter the Email Address login of the Brand Registry user account:账户（咱们是相同账户授权，所以这里就是你的账户）</p>
<p><span>●</span>Enter the brand(s) that this request pertains to:授权的品牌</p>
<p>这种case基本2个小时内处理完成，非常快。</p>
<p>最后看一下这个case品牌团队的回复。</p>
<p>您好，来自Amazon品牌注册支持机构，</p>
<p>多谢您提出要求增加品牌角色的请求。</p>
<p>我可以确认您添加新角色的请求已成功完成：</p>
<p>•要求角色：管理员，权利所有者</p>
<p>这样中东站后台就拥有了创建编辑A+页面的功能。</p>
<p><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201009/86cdce70a6ba4f1fa73182ff2da5a930.png" /></p>
